{
  "text": "For the KendC population, 12 plants per RIL line were planted in a completely randomized design as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] in both long-days and short days at 23uC. The growth conditions and the methodology of flowering time measurements have been described [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
